Class InstructorSchedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • ours.model.InstructorSchedule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Schedule

    public class InstructorSchedule
extends java.lang.Object
implements Schedule
    The InstructorSchedule class is the Schedule class for an Instructor at the University. This class contains the listing of all the Courses that the Instructor teaches.
